mooonpy.doc_examples module

This module shows a few doc string examples for how to write doc strings for automatic Sphinx documentation.

This module will eventually be deleted once all developers understand doc strings and the syntax for sphinx.

The following is a good resource:

https://sphinx-rtd-tutorial.readthedocs.io/en/latest/docstrings.html
